<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>LANDPLUS | 上下水道施設の耐震解析・補強設計</title>
  <meta name="description" content="LANDPLUSの上下水道施設における耐震解析、補強設計、数量計算、概算工事費、図面作成、施工計画書作成に関する技術サービス紹介ページです。" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f4f7fa;
      --paper: #ffffff;
      --ink: #142433;
      --muted: #5d7185;
      --line: #d6dde5;
      --line-strong: #9fb0c1;
      --brand: #173a5e;
      --brand-2: #255b8f;
      --accent: #b38b4d;
      --soft: #edf3f8;
      --soft-2: #f8fbfd;
      --ok: #285d52;
      --shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(12, 31, 52, 0.08);
      --radius-xl: 28px;
      --radius-lg: 20px;
      --radius-md: 14px;
      --content: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Yu Gothic", "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", "Meiryo", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(37, 91, 143, 0.08), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fbfd 0%, #eef4f8 100%);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--content));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .site-header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(248, 251, 253, 0.88);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(159, 176, 193, 0.35);
    }

    .header-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 14px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .brand-sub {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .nav a {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav a:hover {
      background: var(--soft);
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 72px 0 44px;
    }

    .hero-card {
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(23, 58, 94, 0.96), rgba(37, 91, 143, 0.92)),
        #173a5e;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 36px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero-card::before,
    .hero-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-card::before {
      width: 420px;
      height: 420px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      top: -180px;
      right: -120px;
    }

    .hero-card::after {
      width: 240px;
      height: 240px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      bottom: -90px;
      left: -60px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.35fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 28px;
      padding: 54px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.24);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 3.5rem);
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .hero-lead {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .button-primary {
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .button-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      background: #f3f7fb;
    }

    .button-secondary {
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      color: #fff;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .button-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    .hero-panel {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .panel-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .hero-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .hero-list-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: start;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    .hero-list-item:last-child { border-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }

    .hero-num {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
    }

    .hero-list-item strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .hero-list-item span {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    section {
      padding: 26px 0 0;
    }

    .section-block {
      padding: 34px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      color: var(--brand-2);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2.8vw, 2.5rem);
      line-height: 1.3;
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .section-desc {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 880px;
    }

    .overview-grid,
    .service-grid,
    .result-grid,
    .feature-grid,
    .flow-grid,
    .deliverable-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .overview-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr; }
    .service-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .result-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .flow-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .deliverable-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); }

    .card {
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(19, 41, 66, 0.04);
    }

    .card-pad { padding: 28px; }

    .summary-card {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .summary-table {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--line);
    }

    .summary-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .summary-row dt,
    .summary-row dd {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 16px 18px;
    }

    .summary-row dt {
      background: var(--soft-2);
      color: var(--brand);
      font-weight: 700;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .summary-row dd {
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .status-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fbfd 0%, #eef4f8 100%);
    }

    .status-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(40, 93, 82, 0.08);
      color: var(--ok);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
    }

    .status-title {
      margin: 16px 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .check-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .check-list div {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .check-list span {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      flex: 0 0 22px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--brand);
      color: #fff;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .service-card {
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .service-no {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--soft);
      color: var(--brand);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .service-card h3,
    .deliverable-card h3,
    .point-card h3,
    .flow-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      color: var(--brand);
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .service-card p,
    .deliverable-card p,
    .point-card p,
    .flow-card p,
    .metric-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .mini-list {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .mini-list li {
      padding-left: 16px;
      position: relative;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .mini-list li::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0.76em;
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-50%);
    }

    .metric-card {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px 18px;
    }

    .metric-value {
      display: block;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand);
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .metric-label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .point-card,
    .flow-card,
    .deliverable-card {
      height: 100%;
    }

    .point-icon,
    .flow-icon,
    .deliverable-icon {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--soft);
      color: var(--brand);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .process-bar {
      margin-top: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(23,58,94,0.06), rgba(37,91,143,0.12));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .process-track {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .process-step {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      border: 1px solid rgba(159, 176, 193, 0.4);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px 14px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand);
      position: relative;
    }

    .process-step small {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .cta {
      padding: 44px 0 80px;
    }

    .cta-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #173a5e 0%, #214e7c 100%);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 32px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .cta-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta h2 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .cta p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);
    }

    .contact-panel {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .contact-panel dl {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .contact-panel div {
      display: grid;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .contact-panel dt {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.66);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .contact-panel dd {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .site-footer {
      padding: 24px 0 46px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .overview-grid,
      .cta-grid,
      .result-grid,
      .feature-grid,
      .flow-grid,
      .deliverable-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .hero-grid > :first-child,
      .overview-grid > :first-child,
      .cta-grid > :first-child {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
      }

      .service-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .process-track { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .header-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .nav {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 40px;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: 28px;
      }

      .overview-grid,
      .service-grid,
      .result-grid,
      .feature-grid,
      .flow-grid,
      .deliverable-grid,
      .cta-grid,
      .process-track {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .summary-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .summary-row dt {
        border-right: 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .card-pad,
      .cta-card {
        padding: 22px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="#top" class="brand" aria-label="LANDPLUS Home">
        <span class="brand-mark">LANDPLUS</span>
        <span class="brand-sub">Civil Engineering / Seismic Design / Technical Services</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary Navigation">
        <a href="#overview">業務概要</a>
        <a href="#services">業務内容</a>
        <a href="#results">業務成果</a>
        <a href="#points">技術ポイント</a>
        <a href="#flow">対応範囲</a>
        <a href="#contact">お問い合わせ</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="hero-grid">
            <div>
              <div class="eyebrow">Representative Project / Technical Support</div>
              <h1>上下水道施設における<br>耐震解析・補強設計・施工計画支援</h1>
              <p class="hero-lead">
                LANDPLUSは、上下水道施設の既設構造物に対して、耐震解析から補強設計、数量計算、概算工事費、図面作成、施工計画書整理まで、設計から施工準備に至る一連の技術支援を実施。元請会社の業務推進を技術面から支援しました。
              </p>
              <div class="hero-actions">
                <a class="button button-primary" href="#services">業務内容を見る</a>
                <a class="button button-secondary" href="#contact">相談する</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <aside class="hero-panel">
              <div>
                <div class="panel-label">Project Scope</div>
                <div class="hero-list">
                  <div class="hero-list-item">
                    <div class="hero-num">01</div>
                    <div>
                      <strong>耐震解析</strong>
                      <span>三次元的な構造挙動を踏まえ、二次元モデルへ合理的に反映。</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="hero-list-item">
                    <div class="hero-num">02</div>
                    <div>
                      <strong>補強設計</strong>
                      <span>既設条件と施工性を考慮した補強方針・断面検討を実施。</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="hero-list-item">
                    <div class="hero-num">03</div>
                    <div>
                      <strong>施工計画支援</strong>
                      <span>施工順序、留意事項、計画資料整理まで一体で対応。</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="panel-label">Deliverables</div>
                <div style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.8;">
                  数量計算書 / 概算工事費資料 / 設計図面 / 施工計画書
                </div>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="overview" class="section-block">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <span class="section-kicker">Overview</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">対応業務</h2>
          <p class="section-desc">
            既設上下水道施設の耐震性能を確認し、その結果に基づいて補強設計を行うとともに、設計成果として必要となる数量計算、概算工事費、図面、施工計画書までを整理しました。単一作業ではなく、解析・設計・施工準備を一連で支援した点が本案件の特徴です。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-grid">
          <div class="card card-pad summary-card">
            <div>
              <h3 style="margin:0 0 12px; color: var(--brand); font-size: 1.22rem;">プロジェクトサマリー</h3>
              <p style="margin:0; color: var(--muted);">
                客先情報を開示しない形で、技術範囲と成果内容を整理した紹介です。元請会社の設計業務に対して、LANDPLUSが技術支援として対応した範囲を示しています。
              </p>
            </div>
            <dl class="summary-table">
              <div class="summary-row">
                <dt>対象分野</dt>
                <dd>浄水施設・既設構造物・耐震対策</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="summary-row">
                <dt>主な対応</dt>
                <dd>耐震解析、補強設計、施工手順整理</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="summary-row">
                <dt>作成資料</dt>
                <dd>数量計算書、概算工事費資料、図面、施工計画書</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="summary-row">
                <dt>支援形態</dt>
                <dd>元請会社の設計・施工準備業務に対する技術支援</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="card card-pad status-card">
            <span class="status-badge">Integrated Technical Support</span>
            <h3 class="status-title">解析だけで終わらない一体対応</h3>
            <p style="margin:0; color: var(--muted);">
              構造解析の結果を補強設計に反映し、その後の数量・概算・図面・施工計画書まで整理することで、次工程へつながる実務資料として仕上げました。
            </p>
            <div class="check-list">
              <div><span>✓</span><p style="margin:0;">三次元的な受力特性を踏まえた二次元解析モデルの適用</p></div>
              <div><span>✓</span><p style="margin:0;">既設条件と施工条件を踏まえた補強計画</p></div>
              <div><span>✓</span><p style="margin:0;">施工準備に必要な設計資料まで一括整理</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

